Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.33,0:22:39.08,Song,,0,0,0,,I'll never forget, looking up at the sky from this hilltop,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.08,0:22:47.55,Song,,0,0,0,,The morning sun so beautiful, on spring days, just us two.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.52,0:22:55.72,Song,,0,0,0,,All the hardships and the sorrows,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.69,0:23:03.90,Song,,0,0,0,,Carry them away gently from this hilltop,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.57,0:23:10.84,Song,,0,0,0,,together with the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.81,0:23:21.25,Song,,0,0,0,,This vast, blue sky—may it never change,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.25,0:23:30.83,Song,,0,0,0,,And may my dearest friends stay just the way they are.
